React Server Component: https://vercel.com/blog/understanding-react-server-components
We can make few of the components to render on server and few on client.
So to make it to run on server, 'use server"
To make it run on the client, 'use client'.
https://github.com/namastedev/namaste-frontend-system-design/blob/master/Performance/RenderingPatterns/app-router/src/app/tutorial.js
